---
title: Smoky Bacon-Bison Chili with Toasted Tortilla Chips
description: This smoky chili hits all the right notes to warm you up on a chilly night. The double protein dose of bison and bacon makes it extra hearty, while the gooey cheddar cheese takes it to the next level! Scoop up all that tasty goodness with crunchy, spiced tortilla chips.
